遍通行的文字。這樣的語言在反抗「蝗語」(台灣國語或普通話）的壓迫追求自主文化時往往會感覺力不從心。雖然文字化的技術已經沒有問題，可是有音無字的粵語詞語奇多，無所適從，在達成整合共識，解決文字問題，並普及化以前（普及化就是教育，而教育屬政治問題，沒有政治力支持，粵文的普及化可以說不可能），任何香港本土語言都絕對無法和華語文對抗。所以廣東話使用者必需多使用粵文打字,放棄中文"},{"pid":"cae1f155e7ecc76c82ef85ec439b5830e9866a1c","tid":1166052,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"212bb7d8cff86a17aae0b8e7b3812a7d2acd1db3","tid":1166052,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0d69d99d89230137c8e7cec198e6bccfcb86dde4","tid":1166052,"uid":3659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"06d422f26e43ac1fadf0de18819f67c9a92511f5","tid":1166052,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"因為國語係標準語，<br />\n台語只係方言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:18:40.000Z","msg":"原來你係台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋台灣人就叫官話做「國語」啫，你又叫埋一份，係咪弱智？<br />\n又唔見你叫人哋法國嘅法語做國語？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"因為法國係用法文<br />\n但台灣、香港都係用中文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"其實連台灣人都話國語係北京胡語！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/104851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/104851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e9511adf2cb961d14a4d2baa01b56c9b4e8a8f27","tid":1166052,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d76d924a0a565f489a2789aed29857e24bd69772","tid":1166052,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29c7e935435f715e0f43e161e85caf4ed571712b","tid":1166052,"uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"06d422f26e43ac1fadf0de18819f67c9a92511f5","tid":1166052,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"因為國語係標準語，<br />\n台語只係方言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"方你老母言咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 